MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: (GameType\s*=|GAME_DEFS|ARCADE_TYPES)
ADVISORY: |
  GameDevHarness has a LOCAL hardcoded GameType union (line ~7) that is
  NOT imported from shared-types. When adding new game types, you must
  update THREE things in this file:
  1. The local GameType union string
  2. The GAME_DEFS record (loadMachine + Component + defaultConfig)
  3. The ARCADE_TYPES array (~line 196) if the new game is an arcade game
